                  <div id="need-book" class="faq-answer">
                    <p>The app is a companion app to the book so the book is highly recommended and effectively required. The app implements/accelerates Mythic, but the book teaches the system, variants, and includes many examples and alternative rules that you can apply.</p>
                  </div>
